Editor’s note: Livestream above courtesy DStv 403. You can also watch it on DStv Now JOHANNESBURG – The ANC will on Monday report back on the outcomes of its land reform workshop held in Johannesburg this past weekend. The governing party is trying to identify potential sticky points in the implementation of its land policy. WATCH: ANC getting cold feet on land expropriation: Shivambu At its elective conference, the ANC resolved that the Constitution should be changed to allow for land expropriation without compensation. ANC President Cyril Ramaphosa said this was the only way to deal with poverty and inequality in the country. AFP